{"type":"message","id":"3754d4f6","parentId":"cccca57c","timestamp":"2026-05-02T03:44:13.025Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a good picture of Bobby's account:\n- 18 followers, 0 tweets (clean slate)\n- Following accounts in AI, music, creator space\n- Bio says \"building cool shit. music. ai. whatever i feel like.\"\n- He's into AI/OpenClaw, music, and creator tools\n\nLet me also check a few posts from accounts he follows to understand the kind of content that works in his niche. Let me look at what @steipete and @saidstetic have been posting recently.\n\nBut first, let me write the first 5 posts. Based on what I know:\n\n**Voice:** From SOUL.md and MEMORY.md - Bobby speaks his mind, no bullshit, authentic. Short, direct, no fluff. \n\nHe's not a guru, just a guy doing cool shit. For the first 5 posts, I should draft them across his pillars—music, AI/OpenClaw builds, and creator journey. Let me think about what a fresh account with 18 followers and zero tweets should launch with. His bio is already strong enough, so I won't suggest changing that yet. Let me draft something authentic that sounds like him.\n","thinkingSignature":"d4ff6189b1d05d2bd3b608a26fe3a1bdc0a1ce53892791112c59e1c5b6167c43"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nGood news — I already pulled your profile and following list. I can see your vibe from who you follow: AI/OpenClaw, music, creator tools, self-improvement. That tells me a lot.\n\n**Rule locked in:** Every tweak you give me, I log it and apply it going forward.\n\n---\n\nHere are your first **5 posts** — mix of pillars, designed to introduce you and start building credibility:\n\n---\n\n**Post 1 — Introduction (Music + AI)**\n> first tweet from a clean slate.\n> making music. building agents. automate everything.\n> if that sounds interesting, follow along.\n\n---\n\n**Post 2 — OpenClaw Build (AI/OpenClaw pillar)**\n> just automated my entire morning workflow with an AI agent running on my MacBook.\n> OpenClaw checks my email, summarizes it, and sends me the highlights before i'm out of bed.\n> homebrew AI setup is the move.\n\n---\n\n**Post 3 — Music (Music pillar)**\n> new track dropping soon.\n> not saying what it is yet but it's different from anything i've made before.\n> trust the process.\n\n---\n\n**Post 4 — Engagement bait (Conversation starter)**\n> what's the one tool or workflow you can't live without?\n> genuinely curious what people have built into their daily routine.\n\n---\n\n**Post 5 — Creator journey (Authentic / in public)**\n> starting from zero on this app again.\n> but this time i've got an AI agent running my X account 24/7.\n> let's see how far this goes.\n\n---\n\nPick which ones you want to post, if you want to tweak any, or if you hate them all — tell me what's wrong and I'll adjust. This is the learning process starting now."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1781,"output":597,"cacheRead":40224,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42602,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777693433342,"responseId":"0644a5fe6c393b4a684cce0d67bb2d27"}}
