{"type":"message","id":"370fd795","parentId":"7b01aa69","timestamp":"2026-05-02T03:49:18.835Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby's saying hashtags are dead on X - Elon said so. He's offering to have Rex do research on X SEO. I should accept the offer - Rex is the research specialist and it would be good to have up-to-date info on X best practices. I should confirm with Rex what the current best practices are.\n","thinkingSignature":"cebb63b8baf1e7b2156ec8b8764a7c39d947a2eb804554ffa183019239dc8509"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nHa, fair — Elon killed the hashtag era.\n\nYeah, have Rex dig into current X SEO best practices. Would be useful to know what's actually working in 2026 vs dead tactics. Share his findings with me and I'll update my approach accordingly.\n\nAppreciate you keeping me sharp on this stuff. Let's get Rex's research and I'll adjust the playbook."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":42470,"output":138,"cacheRead":192,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42800,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777693749342,"responseId":"0644a735d9b18d8755465b3a30535f27"}}
