{"type":"message","id":"013a6a16","parentId":"d54d3ea1","timestamp":"2026-05-02T03:57:55.419Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see Rex's session. Let me send him a message directly using sessions_send to the rex direct session.","thinkingSignature":"f5009738f1e59b8a5122398a274b995644df93efc685e1243a10527d1e5217f2"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ylkmkan7i61m_1","name":"sessions_send","arguments":{"message":"Hey Rex, need your research skills. Can you look into current X/Twitter SEO best practices for 2026? Specifically: what's working to get posts discovered organically, what tactics are dead (Elon said hashtags are dead), optimal posting patterns, engagement strategies that drive followers, and anything unique to the current X algorithm. Bobby wants to grow his @BobbyGalletta account around music + AI/OpenClaw builds. Send me your findings when you're done.","sessionKey":"agent:rex:telegram:direct:8212808444","timeoutSeconds":120}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3848,"output":172,"cacheRead":47616,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51636,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777694273362,"responseId":"0644a9415a9d32c64e5bae22726958a5"}}
