{"type":"message","id":"cca94624","parentId":"575226e2","timestamp":"2026-05-02T04:15:07.063Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby's concerned about the quality and authenticity of the posts. That's fair - he's not going to let me just post generic AI-written content that doesn't sound like him. \n\nI should show him what posts 2-5 would actually be before scheduling them. He wants to maintain his voice. Let me go through them and explain what each one would be and why they're not random AI slop.\n\nPost 2 was the OpenClaw build one - that makes sense given his actual work.\nPost 3 was the music one.\nPost 4 was the engagement question.\nPost 5 was the creator journey one.\n\nThese are all rooted in things he actually cares about. Let me lay them out for him and get his approval before anything goes out.\n","thinkingSignature":"dc9f754202c242a19dc1905abbe1bf930da1523e81011da749bf48e444539c94"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nGood call — you're right to push back on that.\n\nHere's what 2-5 would be, and why they're not slop:\n\n**Post 2 — OpenClaw build**\nReal thing you actually did: set up an AI agent that handles your morning email before you're awake. This is content from your actual life, not made up.\n\n**Post 3 — Music drop**\nShort, genuine: \"new original track coming soon, different from anything I've made before, stay tuned.\" Rooted in what you're actually working on.\n\n**Post 4 — Engagement question**\n\"what's the one tool or workflow you can't live without?\" — invites real replies, not engagement bait. You get comments, you reply, algorithm loves it.\n\n**Post 5 — Creator journey**\n\"starting from zero on X again, but this time I have an AI agent running my account 24/7.\" — authentic, talks about what you're actually doing here.\n\n---\n\nNone of these are generic AI content. They're all rooted in things you're actually doing or thinking about. The only \"slop\" risk is if I write them in a voice that doesn't sound like you — which is why every tweak you give me, I learn and apply.\n\n**Want to see the actual text for posts 2-5 before I schedule anything?** I'll write them out, you approve or rewrite, then we schedule. No mystery meat in the box."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54849,"output":439,"cacheRead":192,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55480,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777695288298,"responseId":"0644ad3839a8c87ca52b22161472dc1d"}}
