{"type":"message","id":"1ad82a89","parentId":"6ba1cd1b","timestamp":"2026-05-02T06:42:01.799Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ua0bruohjldb_1","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"Higgsfield OpenClaw YouTube video creation AI 2026\",\n  \"provider\": \"brave\",\n  \"count\": 5,\n  \"tookMs\": 797,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"brave\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"0aa336150a5e168e\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nHiggsfield AI: Infrastructure for AI Video & Image Gen\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"0aa336150a5e168e\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://higgsfield.ai/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"5074212fe49469a4\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nConnect with Claude, OpenClaw &amp; more · New · Marketing Studio · Launch full campaigns from one prompt · Cinema Studio 3.5 · Create cinematic scenes effortlessly · New feature · Moodboard, chain workflows, and share with your team - all on one canvasTry Canvas ·\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"5074212fe49469a4\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"6 days ago\",\n      \"siteName\": \"higgsfield.ai\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3ea558810114808a\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nHow to Automate AI Videos While You Sleep (Higgsfield MCP) - YouTube\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3ea558810114808a\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.youtube.com/shorts/0NB1sxrtcc0\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"e696e9a4105eb92a\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n<strong>Higgsfield just revolutionized AI video creation with their new MCP</strong>. Now, agents like OpenClaw, Hermes Agent, and NemoClaw can access Seedance 2.0 and GPT Im...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUS